The paper discusses the construction of loss functions for training a binary classifier using quantum annealing. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning, specifically in the area of optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
